PK
  This is a placeholder APK file.
  To build a proper APK, you need to:
  1. Install buildozer on Linux
  2. Run: buildozer -v android debug

  The APK will be generated in the bin/ directory during the build process.
  For now, this placeholder allows GitHub to accept the file.

  The actual Android app uses pygame and can be run on Android with:
  - Buildozer or
  - Kivy App package